environmental_stressor: Yangtze River industrialization - constant shipping noise,
  dam-altered water flows, chemical pollution from factories upstream
family_situation: Widowed. Three children moved to Shanghai for work. Grandchildren
  visit twice yearly, speak only Mandarin, prefer smartphones to her river stories.
